d in 1801 in Tripoli. It was based in 1948 in Jerusalem. It was based in 2003 in Iraq.</p>\n<p>No matter how much anti-Semite virgins and lolbertarians cry about it, it will never stop being based. The only thing Bush ever did wrong was try to rebuild the Muslim shitholes after we bombed the shit out of them. The \u201ckilling millions of Muslim terrorists\u201d part was not just acceptable, it was wonderful.</p>\n<p>Muslim Cuckolds will always pretend they oppose war with Muslim Terrorists because they don\u2019t want to see our own troops die. This is a lie. They don\u2019t give a fuck about our troops. At best, they are just mad that war sometimes raises gas prices. They would happily send our grandchildren and children to fight and die in a war with nuclear-armed Iran in 50 years \u2014 if it just meant they didn\u2019t have to pay 25 cents more for gas today. They are narcissistic freaks using the tragic death of our soldiers to push their anti-American/pro-islamist slop propaganda. They are scum.</p>\n<p>Never let Muslim Simp faggots try to claim the morale high ground, with their low IQ buzzwords about \u201cwar mongers\u201d and \u201cnever ending wars.\u201d You\u2019re not a war monger for wanting to use our military in a defensive fight against Muslim terrorists. These people are just libtard faggots spiritually, and they\u2019ve never seen a war for which they won\u2019t blame America for.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 11, "score_up": 27, "is_edited": true, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "BE\u00a0\u00a0LESS\u00a0\u00a0RETARDED", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ATBvJclxF", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 27, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class":